==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Siamese
<hw>Si`a*mese`</hw>, <pos>n. sing. & pl.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A native
or inhabitant of Siam; <pluf>pl.</pluf>, the people of Siam.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <singf>sing.</singf> <def>The language of the
Siamese.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

